	if not needed.	Added support for <!-- WebDoc-Page-Revision: $$ -->
	tag.  Changed <!-- WebDoc-Page-Navtrail-Previous-Links: ..--> to
	<!-- WebDoc-Page-Navtrail: ..-->.  Returns all parts by default in
	get_webdoc_parts.  Code cleaning.

