	* modules/miscutil/lib/urlutils.py: Replace "&" by "&amp;" after
	encoding URL arguments in make_canonical_urlargd().  Fixes HTML
	standard compliance issues.  Thanks to Michael Ehrismann for
	reporting the problem.

