2007-03-08  Samuele Kaplun <samuele.kaplun@cern.ch>

	* modules/webaccess/lib/access_control_config.py,
	modules/webaccess/lib/external_authentication_cern.py,
	modules/webmessage/lib/webmessage_dblayer.py,
