2006-09-08  Nikolay Dyankov <ndyankov@gmail.com>

	* modules/bibformat/etc/format_templates/DC.bft,
	modules/bibformat/etc/format_templates/DC.bfx,
	modules/bibformat/etc/format_templates/MARCXML.bfx,
