	* modules/miscutil/sql/tabcreate.sql: Delete superfluous `>'
	characters in the new oaiARCHIVE table definition.

2006-02-01  Gregory Favre <gregory.favre@cern.ch>

	* modules/webmessage/lib/webmessage.py,
