	* modules/websubmit/Makefile.am: Added bin subdir.

2005-03-23  Tibor Simko <tibor.simko@cern.ch>

	* modules/websearch/lib/search_engine.py.wml: Print only one author
	(and eventually et al) for "hs" output format.

